desc_long							评测						“Even if you don't play puzzle games, Monochroma should still entice you with its dark art style, mysterious plot and clever challenges”9/10 – That Video Game Blog“After the emotional roller-coaster Monochroma puts you through, you might wish for a happy ending, but not every ending is pleasant – and sometimes it’s just good enough that something has ended. Play the game all the way through, and you’ll know exactly what I mean.”Indie Game Magazine“Nowhere Studios have proven that games can be a piece of art, and this one will tug at your heart strings.”5/5 – Invision Community												关于这款游戏													
